  <fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a_0]]></fr:tex> be the centre of contraction of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_0]]></fr:tex> be the centre of contraction of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Ba_0]]></fr:tex>. Then we let the centre of contraction of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx]]></fr:tex> be 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen a_0,b_0\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
. The necessary identifications are obtained from the contractibility of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Ba_0]]></fr:tex> by the characterisation of identifications in dependent sums (<fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0035.xml" title="covariant sum of a left-cloven family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0035" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0035" /></fr:link>, <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0017.xml" title="the intrinsic left cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0017" type="local">Example <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0017" /></fr:link>).</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
