            <fr:title text="covariant sum of a left-cloven family of path objects">covariant sum of a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0031.xml" title="left cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0031" type="local">left-cloven family of path objects</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0035.agda" type="external">erct-0035.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
\to  \mathsf {PathObj}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0031.xml" title="left cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0031" type="local">left-cloven family of path objects</fr:link> over a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0010.xml" title="path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0010" type="local">path object</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex>. We define the <html:em><html:strong>covariant sum</html:strong></html:em> of the family <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex>, written <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathcal {B} x}]]></fr:tex>, to be the <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0018.xml" title="the total path object of a displayed path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0018" type="local">total path object</fr:link> of the <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0012.xml" title="displayed path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0012" type="local">displayed path object</fr:link> associated to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0033.xml" title="display of left-cloven families of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0033" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0033" /></fr:link>. In particular, we have defined <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,u\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\approx _{\mathchoice {\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathcal {B} x}}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y,v\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> to be <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}} p_*u \approx _{\mathcal {B} y} v]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
